Title: JShell A lightweight fast graphical shell for windows
Description:
JShell aka Justin Shell is a alternative to Windows Explorer, it provides a interface like Mac and Gnome Its main features are:

JStart a command prompt type start menu
It does not start any of the run registry keys so viruses can take control.
Its lightweight fast booting!
